!important; min-height: auto !important;\">\r\n			<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\" style=\"background: none !important; border-radius: 0px !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; height: auto !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.3em !important; margin: 0px !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; padding: 0px 1em !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; font-size: 1em !important; min-height: auto !important; white-space: pre !important;\"><code>Route::get(</code><code>$uri</code><code>, </code><code>$action</code><code>);</code></div>\r\n\r\n			<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\" style=\"background: none !important; border-radius: 0px !important; border: 0px !important; bottom: auto !important; float: none !important; height: auto !important; left: auto !important; line-height: 1.3em !important; margin: 0px !important; outline: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; padding: 0px 1em !important; position: static !important; right: auto !important; top: auto !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; font-size: 1em !important; min-height: auto !important; white-space: pre !important;\"><code>//trong đó $action có thể là 1 mảng, hàm hoặc 1 chuỗi</code></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"example_wrapper\" style=\"border-radius: 10px 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; padding: 30px 20px 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; background: rgb(247, 247, 249); margin-top: 40px; border: 1px solid rgb(179, 212, 252); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>Cách sử dung</strong></span>:<strong>3</stron